Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Make me one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad used to make them, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I kind of want my own kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't you a bit young for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They make ones for kids, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, eat up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Babies are so cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Kawachi. I'm a relative of Kaga, Rin-san's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-san... Rin's been living with me for awhile now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Yoshii Masako-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to talk to you about in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll happily come to you, so just name a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Place? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder... Perhaps in the shopping district, at{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't actually have any idea where you live...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,More home-made stuff, Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You made this flower, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's called {\i1}embroidery{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a bit older, I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're really good with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say without meeting her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Rin for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you have a good long chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's been looking forward to seeing Rin-chan, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought. It's really close to Granddad's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-smoking, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out. It's going to spill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep getting more and more stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know how that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Americano, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, one Americano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful, Saionji-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just need to give each character a couple of traumatic past events...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it'll be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she go to all the trouble of\Ndisappearing completely from Granddad's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...if she was just going to live right around the corner from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you then, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty careless of someone who's trying to make a getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, I have to pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I know. Just hold on a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Souichi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite. I'm his grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You just looked so much like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else told me that just a little while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Though now that I get a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Souichi-san looked a bit less rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a photo of Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of her from this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at a rice cake making party at her nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, she seems sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...grown up, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody called you "Sensei" back there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the name on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I use that name for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of out of it. It was a busy night last night, and I had to pull an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this job pull you away from Rin, then?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, you convinced Rin that you were the maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But did you do that from the moment she was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... It was because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also true that I was Souichi-san's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had already decided that I wasn't going to think of her as my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...by the time I became pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I don't really understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My work never sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And just as I finally landed a big job,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that I was pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really the sort of job you can have while raising a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But Souichi-san told me I should have the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent my days either working or sleeping, and grew fatter and fatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's strange. When Rin was born, she was so cute, and I couldn't help but love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's strange about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I worked myself to the bone trying to raise her and do my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all along telling myself I wasn't her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was really tough trying to be a day person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of meetings at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...which were impossible to attend unless I was awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I heard Rin spent nights with you at an apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever go out, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, when I said "night", I meant in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd head out once Rin dropped off to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes, I'd have Souichi-san take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin sometimes wakes up in the middle of the night, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you never think about how she'd feel if she woke up to find nobody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But otherwise, how was I supposed to raise a child on my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why Granddad said the three of you should be a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have no objections to me continuing to live with Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer her mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have no right to tell her what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Rin grew inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about her, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she important to you or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have just one favour to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When she goes to school, please let her use your family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My family name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The other kids might give her a hard time if her guardian's name isn't the same as hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you just promise me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand your point,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't promise that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been Kaga Rin all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can just change someone's name like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a woman, so I'm not particularly attached to my family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when it might change, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin's a girl, too, so I'm sure she feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's only six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, that's not really what I'm getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus that's just how you feel, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing that matters here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rin", the name that Souichi-san gave her. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man, so I don't really get what you're saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can talk to her about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's cruel to make a kid\Nthat young decide something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about what's best for Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it'd be more cruel to make that decision for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to ask her what she thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll decide together, and I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just no good. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could abandon such a cute young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely nonsensical!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but she definitely worries about Rin, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that she's a little odd,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or maybe that she doesn't realise the mess she's making for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course a mother's going to worry about her child!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If she really cared, though, she should want to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so rash. She probably has her reasons. Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what your granddad ever saw in her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's kind of the least of our problems right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue at hand is that she asked me to enrol Rin with my family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well I agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that a child should\Nhave the same name as her guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Well, I understand that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to explain that to Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She already has her own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When she gets married, her name will change anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What "again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's just going to go to school and be bullied for her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be better for her to just use ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You think she can just get used to using two names?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are all sorts, even in junior school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll adopt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as she doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she really will be Kawachi Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll be more natural that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk so flippantly about something that important!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not being flippant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have to decide this sooner or later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference if it's now or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It does make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't! It absolutely doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to pass the baton onto anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be too much for Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take anything that comes my way, if it's for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't use it when I'm not around, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can promise me that, you can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I make you curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave it until tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I forget. Do I push? Or pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Give it here a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, you're really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been living on my own for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it slowly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Go in up to your shoulders and count to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:27.65,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Rin says a cute little counting rhyme here in Japanese. The nonsensical words she's saying contain numbers in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Saury and mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Three... Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Burdock and six alligators.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven! Eight! Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat it too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You make really good curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to do it that many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not your big brother, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody thinks {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just giving an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking what you think that makes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... How do I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... How about I become your...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you think if I became your real father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi... as my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we did, your name would be Kawachi Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi... Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better if you had a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the name Kaga Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same name as Granddad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi should just stay as Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweating in March?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened it and you started crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that I wasn't crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Move your head up a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this'll always be your home from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We shouldn't forget what we believe in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because morning is always just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We shouldn't give up on our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll all come true someday, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first step forward;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a step towards tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Starting today, everything is new!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first step forward;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a step toward tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gather your courage, and take a big step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. I'm a waste of a human being, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Only kids get hugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Sayaka-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even adults have times when they want someone to hug them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're adults! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be okay, even once I'm in first grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hug you whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've hugged you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hug you next time you cry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting to the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...where I'm losing track of whether I'm raising Rin,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether she's raising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly through the sky, pass through the water and run over the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm called Kaga Rin. {Here she uses a very old japanese, looks like she is talking like a ninja or samurai}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I start 1st grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I want to be a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi taught me about a secret training technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First we need to plant a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see more next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The next story is "My Tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose?
